title: Sky-Dome: Leveling to Supreme
summary: Sky-Dome: Leveling to Supreme Manhua The youngster, Jiang Yinian, became acquaintances with Mu Chen, Lin Dong, and Xiao Yan’s descendants on the Spirit Road’s Trial, and also stole someone’s heart, too. In the process of the trials he realized that he had connections to the Fiend Clan that had been sealed in the Prison Realm, and so, the story begins… Holy Saint Shengling Ji Heaven’s List: Saint’s Era Spirit’s Story The Heaven’s List Thương Khung Bảng 圣灵纪 苍穹榜之圣灵纪 苍穹榜：圣灵纪 蒼穹榜之聖靈紀
